{"parentUuid":"952b351c-ed59-4037-b028-a9d8ed961d1b","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"c1e8f266-6f4b-4088-b12c-56744b46be3e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017V5ZCWmRpbJjEuQNW3C8T8","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→CREATE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at()\n     2→RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\n     3→BEGIN\n     4→  NEW._updated_at = NOW();\n     5→  RETURN NEW;\n     6→END;\n     7→$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n     8→\n     9→\n    10→CREATE EXTENSION ltree;\n    11→\n    12→CREATE TABLE \"categories\" (\n    13→    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    14→    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    15→    path ltree NOT NULL,\n    16→\n    17→    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    18→    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n    19→);\n    20→\n    21→CREATE TABLE \"authors\" (\n    22→    author_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    23→    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    24→    profile TEXT NOT NULL,\n    25→\n    26→    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    27→    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n    28→);\n    29→\n    30→CREATE TABLE \"courses\" (\n    31→    course_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    32→    title TEXT NOT NULL,\n    33→    description TEXT NOT NULL,\n    34→    slug TEXT NOT NULL,\n    35→    tags JSONB NOT NULL,\n    36→    publish_status TEXT NOT NULL,\n    37→    category_id UUID NOT NULL,\n    38→    published_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    39→    last_updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,\n    40→    author_id UUID NOT NULL,\n    41→\n    42→    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    43→    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    44→\n    45→    CONSTRAINT fk_courses_category_id FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES categories(category_id),\n    46→    CONSTRAINT fk_courses_author_id FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES,\n    47→    CONSTRAINT uq_courses_slug_author_id UNIQUE (slug, author_id)\n    48→);\n    49→\n    50→CREATE TRIGGER trigger_courses_meta_updated_at\n    51→    BEFORE UPDATE ON courses\n    52→    FOR EACH ROW\n    53→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n    54→\n    55→CREATE TRIGGER trigger_categories_meta_updated_at\n    56→    BEFORE UPDATE ON categories\n    57→    FOR EACH ROW\n    58→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n    59→\n    60→CREATE TRIGGER trigger_authors_meta_updated_at\n    61→    BEFORE UPDATE ON authors\n    62→    FOR EACH ROW\n    63→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n    64→\n    65→COMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n    66→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"uuid":"f3ec15e7-b06b-470b-9792-a6bb141d9e73","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:36:28.189Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku/apps/api/migrations/000001_add_courses.up.sql","content":"CREATE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n  NEW._updated_at = NOW();\n  RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\n\nCREATE EXTENSION ltree;\n\nCREATE TABLE \"categories\" (\n    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    path ltree NOT NULL,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE \"authors\" (\n    author_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    profile TEXT NOT NULL,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE \"courses\" (\n    course_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    title TEXT NOT NULL,\n    description TEXT NOT NULL,\n    slug TEXT NOT NULL,\n    tags JSONB NOT NULL,\n    publish_status TEXT NOT NULL,\n    category_id UUID NOT NULL,\n    published_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    last_updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,\n    author_id UUID NOT NULL,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n\n    CONSTRAINT fk_courses_category_id FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES categories(category_id),\n    CONSTRAINT fk_courses_author_id FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES,\n    CONSTRAINT uq_courses_slug_author_id UNIQUE (slug, author_id)\n);\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_courses_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON courses\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_categories_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON categories\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_authors_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON authors\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n\nCOMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n","numLines":66,"startLine":1,"totalLines":66}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"952b351c-ed59-4037-b028-a9d8ed961d1b","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b25d7d57-e366-43a2-be3f-9a40ab32fca2","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"sequential-meandering-fountain"}
{"parentUuid":"f3ec15e7-b06b-470b-9792-a6bb141d9e73","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019sRgiEt1Etnfa2C2U7VuNo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"レビュー結果です。\n\n---\n\n### バグ\n\n**46行目: `FOREIGN KEY` 参照先が未記述**\n\n```sql\nCONSTRAINT fk_courses_author_id FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES,\n```\n\n`REFERENCES` の後に参照テーブル・カラムが欠けています。\n\n```sql\nCONSTRAINT fk_courses_author_id FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES authors(author_id),\n```\n\n---\n\n### ルール違反（`CLAUDE.md` / `migrations/CLAUDE.md` 基準）\n\n1. **`categories` と `authors` にトリガーはあるが、`authors` テーブルにはトリガーが存在する一方、`categories` もあるので問題なし** — これは OK。\n\n2. **`CREATE EXTENSION ltree` に `IF NOT EXISTS` がない**  \n   冪等性を保つため推奨（必須かはプロジェクトルール次第ですが、二回実行するとエラーになります）:\n   ```sql\n   CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS ltree;\n   ```\n\n---\n\n### 設計上の懸念\n\n- `courses.last_updated_at` と `_updated_at` が役割的に重複している可能性があります。`_updated_at` はメタカラムで自動更新されますが、`last_updated_at` が「コースコンテンツの最終更新日」を意図しているなら意図を明確にするか、コメントを追加すると良いです。\n\n- `courses.tags JSONB NOT NULL` — タグを JSONB で持つ設計は問題ないですが、空配列 `'[]'` が許容されるのかどうかはアプリ側で担保する前提として OK です。\n\n---\n\n### 修正必須\n\n46行目のみ確実なバグです。修正しますか?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":946,"cache_read_input_tokens":7269,"output_tokens":506,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":946,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJm49SKjy88XehcF7DTw","type":"assistant","uuid":"043d9e44-8a55-489e-ad9c-7eb3f04841f3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:36:39.447Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b25d7d57-e366-43a2-be3f-9a40ab32fca2","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"sequential-meandering-fountain"}
